down.Fitness CenterDo not waste your timeThey give a lot of points but when you order from their gift catalog ignore the pictures as you will not get what is depicted in the picture. You will receive a product but not what is depicted in the photo. Not worth the shabby treatment. I would rather spend my money someplace where they make you feel welcome. Keep in mind I have VIP/High Roller status here so I got the best of what they had to offer for free and it was still certainly not worth it. One more thing... complain about anything and you will very diplomatically be blown off	
