roup but the comps go a lot further at other locations - free breakfast most days from gambling the night before on our way out to see the town - decatur or boulder depending on which direction you are going. The comps don't go far (if any) in Stratosphere and to be quite frank we have not found the food or restaurants to be that good at Strat anyways - so we usually eat elsewhere with ACG coupons.	
